* * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
Welcome to Psalm 144 Rules Channel!
 
> We encourage activity among our members but understand that life happens. 

> We expect some donations during the week. 

> Consistently having 0 (zero) donations might get you demoted or kicked,
however consistently having 300+ in a week might lead to a promotion.  

> Joining Clan Wars is NOT Required:
     However, if you do join in a of the fun of a Clan War we expect:
          1) All Collection Day and,
          2) War Aay Attacks to be completed. 
     Not completing Collection Day and War Day attacks might result in a demotion, or kicking.
     If you do not complete Collection Day and Way Day attacks we expect to here a reason to be mentioned.
     We get that life happens, but we have to be informed. 

> All promotions take time for trust to be built. 

> Be active and participate and you should do well in this clan.

Once again ${tempVars("NewMemberJoin")}, Welcome!!!

At anytime you wish to review the rules type %Rules on the ${tempVars("NewMemberRules")} channel
